# Guarantee (co-safety, F-reachable)
# AP-renamed to canonical a,b,c… (the curated 40-formula survey corpus)

a  # single-letter guarantee; smallest non-trivial case
X a  # depth ladder: 3-level cascade
X X a  # depth ladder: 4-level cascade
X X X a  # depth ladder: 5-level cascade
X(a & X a)  # depth ladder: branching next, 5-level
Fa  # pure reachability; smallest liveness
a U b  # until: the canonical guarantee with a hold condition
F(a & b)  # reach a boolean state
F(a & X b)  # reach-then-next; a former equiv residual (reach-driven)
a | X b  # boolean over a next; shallow co-safety
